<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sidebar</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.11.8/dist/umd/popper.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-I7E8VVD/ismYTF4hNIPjVp/Zjvgyol6VFvRkX/vR+Vc4jQkC+hVqc2pM8ODewa9r"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-0pUGZvbkm6XF6gxjEnlmuGrJXVbNuzT9qBBavbLwCsOGabYfZo0T0to5eqruptLy"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            display: flex;
            min-height: 100vh;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f5f5, #e3e3e3);
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        }

        /* Sidebar Styles */
        .glass-sidebar {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 250px;
            height: 100vh;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px 0 rgba(31, 38, 135, 0.37);
            border-right: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
            padding: 20px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
            z-index: 999;
        }

        .glass-sidebar:hover {
            width: 280px;
        }

        .glass-sidebar h2 {
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .glass-sidebar .nav-link {
            color: #fff;
            margin: 15px 0;
            font-size: 18px;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .glass-sidebar .nav-link:hover {
            color: #0d6efd;
        }

        .glass-sidebar .nav-link.active {
            color: #0d6efd;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        /* Content Styles */
        .content {
            margin-left: 270px;
            padding: 40px;
            flex-grow: 1;
        }

        .content h1 {
            font-size: 36px;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .content p {
            color: #555;
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <!-- Sidebar -->
    <div class="glass-sidebar">
        <h2>My Sidebar</h2>
        <ul class="nav flex-column">
            <li class="nav-item">
                <a class="nav-link active" href="#"><i class="fas fa-home"></i>Home</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
                <a class="nav-link" href="#"><i class="fas fa-user"></i>About</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
                <a class="nav-link" href="#"><i class="fas fa-cogs"></i>Services</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
                <a class="nav-link" href="#"><i class="fas fa-briefcase"></i>Portfolio</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
                <a class="nav-link" href="#"><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>Contact</a>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="content">
        <h1>Welcome to My Page</h1>
        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nulla id dolor quis arcu dignissim fermentum. Proin
            a eros nisi. Mauris euismod, erat non tincidunt tempor, magna risus dictum felis, non vulputate ligula est a
            velit. Quisque rutrum leo nec libero consequat, in tincidunt magna aliquet. Sed eget diam velit. Donec
            blandit consectetur arcu, ac varius quam ullamcorper a.</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>